# Function Pointers

Given:

```text
rdi = function pointer
```

Call it:

```asm
call rdi
ret
```

Equivalent:

```c
callback();
```

---

# Function Pointer With Arguments

Given:

```text
rdi = callback pointer
```

Need:

```c
callback(1337);
```

Solution:

```asm
mov rax, rdi
mov rdi, 1337
call rax
ret
```

