# argc / argv Layout

Program start:

```text
[rsp]      = argc
[rsp+8]    = argv[0]
[rsp+16]   = argv[1]
[rsp+24]   = argv[2]
```

Read argc:

```asm
mov rdi, [rsp]
```

Read argv[1]:

```asm
mov rdi, [rsp+16]
```

First character:

```asm
mov al, [rdi]
```

