# Jump Tables

Pattern:

```asm
xor eax, eax
mov al, [rcx]
mov rax, [rax*8 + table]
jmp rax
```

Meaning:

```c
goto jump_table[input];
```

Useful GDB:

```gdb
x/a ADDRESS
x/20a ADDRESS
```

